Tune in to @BishopJakes, one of the most transformational leaders of our time on #KingdomCulture every Sunday at 9AM and 12PM EST only on @RevoltTV!!

node.text: I’ve spent the last 10 years in and out of a dark place, struggling to find the meaning in everything happening to me and around me. I stepped away from music, I moved across the country, and tried to escape the heartbreak I was feeling. I needed to get off the floor, get up and get closer to GOD! And really discover my reason for being here!
